text: Irene Ivancan (born 22 July 1983) is a German table tennis player, born in Stuttgart. She competed in women's team at the 2012 Summer Olympics in London. ==References== ==External links== * * * * Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Stuttgart Category:German female table tennis players Category:Olympic table tennis players of Germany Category:Table tennis players at the 2012 Summer Olympics
